{"article_id":"VZgGSlSboO3cC4eD","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump slammed James Comey on Friday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"for denying in a Fox News interview","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that his decision","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"to share memos","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"detailing his conversations with the president","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"constituted a leak","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"- saying","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"his former FBI director is \" either very sick or very dumb . \"","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"Comey ,","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"whom Trump fired in May 2017 ,","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"denied Thursday","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"that sharing the memos with his legal team constituted a leak of classified information .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"`` I did n't consider it part of an FBI file , ''","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"Comey told Fox News ' Bret Baier during an appearance on \" Special Report.","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"\" He compared the process","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"to keeping a \" diary \"","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"and maintained","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"a key memo \" was unclassified then . \"","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"But ,","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"as Fox News has previously reported ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"the Justice Department inspector general is looking into Comey ' s handling of the memos","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"- and Comey acknowledged in the interview","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"that the IG has interviewed him .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Trump ,","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"who earlier Thursday claimed","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Comey was \" guilty of crimes , \"","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"fired back Friday on Twitter .","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"\" Is everybody believing what is going on .","depth":4},{"id":28,"text":"James Comey can ' t define what a leak is .","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"He illegally leaked CLASSIFIED INFORMATION","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"but doesn ' t understand what he did","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"or how serious it is .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"He lied all over the place","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"to cover it up .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"He ' s either very sick or very dumb .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"Remember sailor ! \"","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"he wrote .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"His mention of the \" sailor \" apparently was a reference to Kristian Saucier , the former U.S. Navy sailor","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"who served a year behind bars","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"for taking photos of classified areas in a nuclear submarine .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Trump recently pardoned him .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Comey , in the Fox News interview , acknowledged giving the memos to at least three people","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"including his friend , Columbia University law professor Daniel Richman .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"he sent Richman a copy of the two-page unclassified memo","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"and \" asked him to get the substance of it out to the media \"","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"-- which he did .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"\" The reason","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"I 'm smiling , Bret , \"","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Comey said ,","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"\" I do n't consider","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"what I shared Mr. Richman a leak . \"","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Testifying before the Senate Intelligence Committee last year ,","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"Comey said","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"he made the decision","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"to document his interactions with Trump in a way","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"that would not trigger security classification .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"He also testified","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"that he avoided putting classified material in the memos","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"so that they could be more widely shared .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"The Wall Street Journal , however , reported","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"that at least two of those memos have been to found to contain material","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"now deemed classified ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"prompting the inspector general investigation .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"In the seven total memos","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"handed over to congressional committees ,","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"eight of the 15 pages have redactions under classified exceptions .","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"They include classified information at one of the most sensitive levels","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"-- SECRET --","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"as well as the lower level of confidential .","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"In one memo","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"documenting his January 2017 Trump Tower meeting ,","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Comey wrote","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"that the material should be classified at the SECRET level","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"unless the intelligence agencies thought otherwise .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"\" I am not sure of the proper classification here , \"","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"Comey wrote ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"\" so have chosen SECRET .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Please let me know","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"if it should be higher or lower than that . \"","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":159,"left":102,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":87,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":85,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":0,"right":84,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":1,"right":83,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":83,"left":82,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":82,"left":2,"right":81,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nucl